{"tid":996242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑我溝緊條女有人格分裂","createTime":"2019-01-26T06:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T11:57:31.000Z","uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4e9a068d6a2ca302ab5526a16bded553464b2d","tid":996242,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"我懷疑我溝緊條女有人格分裂<br />\n每星期轉一次人格<br />\n一個中意我, 一個唔中意我<br />\n<br />\n我同條女識咗四個月到<br />\n大家都互相對對方有好感<br />\n但女方係主動d嘅<br />\n幾乎每次都係佢約我出街（食嘢我埋單）<br />\n<br />\n雖然我表咗白<br />\n但佢話相處多排先再正式一齊<br />\n<br />\n但好奇怪係有個循環<br />\n佢有時幾乎日日想見我<br />\n但有時約極都唔肯出/放飛機<br />\n甚至話以後whatsapp 聯絡唔好見<br />\n<br />\n不過過一排又冇事, 又狂約我（我冇哄返佢㗎）<br />\n之後又話好忙唔出 （我冇做錯事）<br />\n又重覆講呢句: 以後whatsapp 聯絡唔好見<br />\n不斷輪迴...<br />\n<br />\n到底發生咩事? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e24d9be868cb2c80cf62abe2f5c34fc57d7461c","tid":996242,"uid":66402,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"兵<br />\n完"},{"pid":"bfcd34ee8bb5af7a0071bb2a4b4e7d42f80ad75b","tid":996242,"uid":94828,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"冇野嘅 約咗另一條仔啫"},{"pid":"360b8a9d5bee3fb50552eccb0a78248b0313ef93","tid":996242,"uid":134997,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"同緊另一條仔扯貓尾<br />\n利申 另一條仔"},{"pid":"15f022259800324cb357ecb03072ed8f13e691b8","tid":996242,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"有仔咪叫你唔好再見囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79212f3614c2c196d93974969e1d4b86bee77ee","tid":996242,"uid":190657,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:38:45.000Z","msg":"sip時間"},{"pid":"f08742ba97390d99cee5af53562771c176746b89","tid":996242,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"咁既囡執到喊三聲啦<img src=\"/assets/fa